    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to middle period of Neolithic culture, which occurred roughly 5500 to 4500 BCE in Europe, and at other times elsewhere in the world.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
